{"tid":1368654,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係咪唔記得咩叫 兄弟爬山","createTime":"2019-07-26T14:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T17:04:02.000Z","uid":115041,"like":246,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"b2a811e342c66f1616d353766e312397a53be7df","tid":1368654,"uid":115041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:01:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVEUhAVki0DA&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07i%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=51893eb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA</a><br />\n<br />\n所謂兄弟爬山，係繼續做自己相信既抗爭方式，但絕<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不割蓆，不分化啊！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你相信和平抗爭，繼續做！<br />\n如果你相信勇武行動，繼續做！<br />\n如果你相信絕食，按自己身體情況去做！<br />\n<br />\n但大家<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">互相擁護！</span>，而唔係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">互相指責同控制！</span><br />\n<br />\n如果和理非手足俾人打，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武手足去保護！</span><br />\n如果勇武手足俾人挑釁，出左手，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請和理非大力做文宣工作，帶風向，保護返勇武手足！</span><br />\n<br />\n如果6月9號同16號，冇大量和理非，會唔會令香港人團結起來？<br />\n<br />\n如果612冇勇武手足，又阻唔阻到條例通過？<br />\n<br />\n如果冇文宣巴打，會唔會有咁有效既方法俾香港人知發生緊咩事？<br />\n<br />\n所以大家！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化，不割蓆！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港！時代革命！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>一齊贏一次，好唔好？</strong></span>"},{"pid":"7c28558edee0dff455b0c5440368b988ed24694b","tid":1368654,"uid":115041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:01:53.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"668de0176158ccdb29579b61c3a8e649b9d836e5","tid":1368654,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:04:20.000Z","msg":"今次就係和理非同勇武一齊出來勝利遊行<br />\n幾時見過勝行遊行都打仗咁<br />\n係咪？"},{"pid":"49bfc172d8683d688675003bd12928b0d24959e2","tid":1368654,"uid":108074,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14: